KEYS IN GAME
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
Left mouse button to select the tile
Right mouse button to active help
Both mouse buttons to deselect the tile
P key to pause
M key to enable or disable the game music
Esc key or click on the top-left corner gadget to quit



FEATURES
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
15 different levels
Useful HELP mode for beginners
Automatic check of a premature end-of-the-game (no free tiles to remove)
32 colors screens
4 different modules
Superb SFX
Full game loaded at start on machines with 1Mb chip or more
Hi-scores saving
Possibility to load "new tiles-set" before to start



SWITCHES
¯¯¯¯¯¯¯¯
START        Click here to play the game

HELP ON/OFF  Enable/disable use of the help-mode in the game. With HELP ON
             you will have 3 available help for each level but a lower
             bonus score at the end of the game

TIME ON/OFF  Enable/disable the time-limit in the game. With TIME ON you
             will achieve higher scores

ABOUT        Some infos about the authors

HIGH-SCORES  Display the high-scores screen

QUIT         Guess what?




